# Supabase Phase 2 (planned)

> **Status:** Phase 2 not started. `src/app/(app)/` does not exist yet. Apply this rule only when scaffolding the web panel.

## Scope split

- **Official Supabase plugin skill:** RLS, migrations, security checklist, MCP/CLI usage.
- **This repo:** Next.js layout, route guards, env wiring, HalıSaha-specific routes.

Do not duplicate Supabase security docs here — reference the plugin skill.

## Client setup

- Use `@supabase/ssr` with cookie-based sessions for App Router.
- Public env only: `NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL`, `NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY` (see `.env.example`).
- Never expose `service_role` in client or `NEXT_PUBLIC_*` vars.

## Authorization

- RLS on all exposed tables; policies match halisaha-organizer schema.
- Do not authorize from `user_metadata` JWT claims.

## Repo layout (when implementing)

```
src/app/(app)/
  layout.tsx      # session check, redirect unauthenticated
  ...
src/lib/supabase/
  server.ts       # createServerClient for RSC
  client.ts       # browser client (client components only)
```

